{"id":133407,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/01/书陶潜《命子》（选四章）/","date":"2011-01-23T13:40:23Z","modified":"2011-01-23T13:40:23Z","title":"书陶潜《命子》（选四章）","content":"<p><p align=\"center\"><span>（岁在庚寅腊月己巳，吾家虎崽出谷，书靖节先生诗</span><span></p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div><span></p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span></p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"http://blogfile.ifeng.com/uploadfiles/blog_attachment/1101/14/1218514_003ccb1c17614afe23b4e0b9a3555e7f.jpg\" /></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></span><span>。）</span></p>\n<p align=\"center\">嗟余寡陋，瞻望弗及。顾惭华鬓，负影只立。三千之罪，无后为急。我诚念哉，呱闻尔泣。</p>\n<p align=\"center\">卜云嘉日，占亦良时。名汝曰俨，字汝求思。温恭朝夕，念兹在兹。尚想孔伋，庶其企而！</p>\n<p align=\"center\">厉夜生子，遽而求火。凡百有心，奚特于我！既见其生，实欲其可。人亦有言，斯情无假。</p>\n<p align=\"center\">日居月诸，渐免于孩。福不虚至，祸亦易来。夙兴夜寐，愿尔斯才。尔之不才，亦已焉哉！</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<h4>要翻墙? <a href=\"http://83920.info\">用赛风</a>.</h4>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[8800]}